caption:
Father's Day is fast approaching, and did you know that you can choose to treat your father to a unique experience at Bombay Brow Bar? 👀 

He can choose whether to have his eyebrows done, get a facial marma massage, or have a custom bear grooming with our a-la-carte services. 🤓

Surprise him a gift card or book an appointment at one of our four locations in Vancouver (link in bio 🔗 or visit: https://zcu.io/EESi ), so he can  get a 'him' time this Father's Day. ✨💖
